				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/D%E1%BB%A5-ch%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C4%83n/poem-j9Hfw5Qp2ojck3M3yZbHSw">Dụ chư tỳ tướng hịch văn - 諭諸裨將檄文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-B3gaZnYZj3Y7n162MsC6mQ">Trần Quốc Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Th%E1%BA%A5t-Thuy%E1%BA%BFt/%C4%90%C3%A0-m%C3%A3-h%E1%BB%AFu-ho%C3%A0i/poem-Ogxq1mXmVse8Aq2BDFPQEg">Đà mã hữu hoài - 馱馬有懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Th%E1%BA%A5t-Thuy%E1%BA%BFt/author-ZOpZ46P49J3Ico14TJrZJg">Tôn Thất Thuyết</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/%C4%90%C3%A1o-B%C3%A0nh-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-q5JIsZq7_msCA4s06yKonA">Đáo Bành Thành - 到彭城</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BA%A7u-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Kha-Th%C6%B0-khai-ph%E1%BB%A7-H%C3%A0n-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-5ObPm0_Kbb60En8Le2b_mg">Đầu tặng Kha Thư khai phủ Hàn nhị thập vận - 投贈哥舒開府翰二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Tuy%C3%AAn-Ch%C3%A2u-Khai-Nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%B1-tr%C3%AD-%C6%B0-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-T%E1%BA%A5n-th%C3%AC/poem-vD7r3eBbK0uI4eWOqyY6ew">Đề Tuyên Châu Khai Nguyên tự, tự trí ư Đông Tấn thì - 題宣州開元寺，寺置於東晉時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-Ho%C3%A0ng-L%E1%BB%97-Tr%E1%BB%B1c-thi/poem-69XciftFryS12VW0lSMp0g">Độc Hoàng Lỗ Trực thi - 讀黃魯直詩</a> (<a href